            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>I‚Äôm not quite there yet (being able to change features in Redash). Still struggling with Redash VMs: my development vm is not working.</p>
<p>But I‚Äôve made some changes in my local Redash 7 (bitnami VM) and I‚Äôm trying to publish these changes in docker production Redash:</p>
<ul>
<li>hide filters on widgets when dashboard uses global filters</li>
<li>filters use 4 columns instead of 6 on dashboards and widgets (so I can have three filters on each line). In truth, I‚Äôd like to be able to change filters‚Äô appearance;</li>
<li>add id to each widget so I can use &lt;a href="<span class="hashtag">#id</span>"&gt; inside fixed-text widgets (think of menu or ‚Äúback to top‚Äù links);</li>
</ul>
<p>Bye for now,</p>
<p>Arnaldo</p>
